{"tid":1281751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我求下你地 唔好做傻事","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:29:43.000Z","uid":266260,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3405761d243321bd6c6442e83e60b6eb7b4bf3ff","tid":1281751,"uid":266260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"我對呢個香港都好絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢發到工都辭埋<br />\n就係希望 我小小嘅力量 可以改變到小小嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係犧牲左條命 木木奠都唔會可憐你 而撤回<br />\n我地一齊努力好冇？<br />\n唔好做傻事好冇？<br />\n我地一齊爭取 我地想得到嘅野好冇？"},{"pid":"35093abe20396a9e2cbbd0b05b74ca5e7ebf273e","tid":1281751,"uid":268497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"唔好向絕望屈服 直到黎明到來之前 忍耐吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbcfb4e873441e2ccd445d42dc70bceb5f44e48","tid":1281751,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"一早辭左"},{"pid":"f2f25c65332de68b81de1d86a71a5d2c4868adbf","tid":1281751,"uid":153160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"未輸架 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb86be6ed8df19d63daa439d851c50e1c900b012","tid":1281751,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"大力推。我哋宜家贏係贏長命呀，保住自己條命，讀好書，他日先有機會奪權做主嫁<br />\n<br />\n(毅進妹，我哋又見喇，你近排ok?"},{"pid":"2e794f0b3b385d198ef15408f19459781d5c45c2","tid":1281751,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"LMF - 惡世紀<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8aXg6t1aiXg&amp;list=RD8aXg6t1aiXg&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8aXg6t1aiXg%26list%3DRD8aXg6t1aiXg%26start_radio%3D1&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a69882d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8aXg6t1aiXg&amp;list=RD8aXg6t1aiXg&amp;start_radio=1</a><br />\n<br />\n維權既道路點會平坦<br />\n太野蠻莫須有剝奪你自由<br />\n犧牲咗嘅生命永遠冇得返轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖個白最邋遢<br />\n玩到咁串點算有無彎轉<br />\n俾人捉住痛腳仲要死猛兜圈<br />\n插到佢氣喘要搵窿捐<br />\n邊個勇士送佢一程我送花圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820fd7704dd3e4bc2871a68965955cdf86c4717d","tid":1281751,"uid":138987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3sk4f7sGDJc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3sk4f7sGDJc&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=958e836c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3sk4f7sGDJc</a><br />\n珍惜生命"},{"pid":"fe13c6d4f378bdcebb30fd06d5f9bd3f685c5e66","tid":1281751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"死幾多人班仆街政府官員都唔會理<br />\n不如留返條命，發展專業，進佔社會高層<br />\n以待時機報復"},{"pid":"c909e41d711994cccb14e81eb60459dd44e4ddcd","tid":1281751,"uid":74122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"岩啊 <br />\n要一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be6657bcb5f881bba0254d141aa9985d7a7be42","tid":1281751,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"好多手足都已經好攰架喇，唔好再要佢地撲黎撲去拉你地返黎啦，一個都不能少呀！"},{"pid":"528ab4a65941147fc8d0753d880e7e6c6f36727c","tid":1281751,"uid":43991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"我地少一個人就係少一個人抗爭<br />\n場仗就越來越難打<br />\n所以各位巴絲打撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔女大把同路人<br />\n我地要一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}